1. Make sure python is install on machine
Check using ==> python --version

2. Make sure pip is install on machine
To install ==> python -m ensurepip --default-pip
Check using ==> pip --version

3. install selenium
==> pip install selenium

4. install webdriver
==> pip install webdriver_manager

5. Installing selenium with webdriver manager
==> pip install selenium webdriver_manager

6. To verify webdriver-manager
==> pip show webdriver-manager

Pytest Framework
install
==> pip install -U pytest

upgrade
==> python.exe -m pip install --upgrade pip


check version
==> pytest --version

to run markers
==> pytest -m regression

to show all markers
==>  pytest --markers

to run markers
==> pytest -m regression -v

to install pytest-html

pip install pytest-html


